---
layout: post
title:  "European Week of Regions and Cities 2017"
date: 2017-10-09 to 2017-10-12
imageurl: 'images/events/European Week of Regions and Cities Logo.png'
location: "Brussels, Belgium"
---
Between 9 and 12 October 2017, the Brussels-based European Week of Regions and Cities programme will feature:

an Opening Session on 9 October at the European Parliament (tbc);
over 100 workshops and debates, organised by organisers and event partners and managed jointly with them, including University workshops;  
a Master Class for PhD students in regional policy;
RegioStars Awards Ceremony and Official Reception;
a media programme;
networking facilities.

[For more information](http://ec.europa.eu/regional_policy/regions-and-cities/2017/index.cfm){:target="_blank"}
